  <!-- Start Update Input -->
  <h1 align="center">It's been awhile,<br>but we are still on a roll!</h1>
<div align="center"> 
  <table width="550" border="0">
    <tr> 
      <td height="110"> <p>I know, its been a long time, but I must say we have 
          been kicking serious ass. In addition to the many Plane of Time clearings 
          we have done, we have also been managing to keep the Elemental gods 
          down too. So instead of boring you with a bunch of corpse shots, I thought 
          I would show you how amazing Quarm has been to us. Why Quarm? Well because 
          we want to brag I guess and we simply can't get enough of this guy. 
        </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<p align="center"><img src="http://www.furysedge.com/news/031211/121103v2.jpg" width="550" height="392"></p>

<div align="center">
  <table width="550" border="0">
    <tr> 
      <td><p>This isn't everything. The loot has just been rolling in, its hard 
          to keep up since the last update and on top of that, its simply too 
          much to list. Lets just say, Time has been good to us. Grats to everyone 
          that got loot, you all deserved it. </p>
        <p>Now, in addition to getting many Leather, Silk and Chain breastplates, 
          I would like to brag a little bit. For the past 3 Rallos Zek kills, 
          he has given us 6 Plate Breastplates. Yes 6. Thats two BP's per kill. 
          Also in the process of making this update, he dropped another one. Congrats 
          to Torahdane, Sharnhorst, Cephas, Galgamesh, Solwene, &amp; Linara on 
          those lucky 6, and grats to Charitey who got her new BP tonight. Lets 
          hope this pattern continues! </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div align="center">
  <table width="550" border="0">
    <tr> 
      <td><p align="left">Now for our little plug...</p>
        <p>Are you a Cleric looking for a new home?
		Do you want to spend 5-6 days a week keeping
        some of the best players in EQ alive?
        Do you want to kill the toughest mobs out there 
        and maybe upgrade your gear in the process?</p>
        <p>If so we would love to see you apply. Fury's 
          Edge is now recruiting <strong>Clerics.</strong> We need dedicated players 
          who will log in night after night with bells on. For more information 
          on what we are looking for and how to apply please
		  <a href="http://www.furysedge.com/apply.cfm">click here.</a> </p>
        </td>
